sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway API Gateway<br/>Envoy Proxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ExtProc as Payload Processing<br/>ExtProc Server<br/>9004/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant ModelResolver as model-provider-resolver<br/>Plugin
    participant APITranslate as api-translation<br/>Plugin
    participant APIKey as apikey-injection<br/>Plugin
    participant NemoReq as nemo-request-guard<br/>Plugin (optional)
    participant NemoResp as nemo-response-guard<br/>Plugin (optional)
    participant NemoSvc as NeMo Guardrails<br/>HTTP plaintext
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant LLM as External LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over ExtProc,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Startup - ExternalModel/Secret Reconciliation
    K8sAPI-->>ModelResolver: Watch ExternalModel CRDs<br/>SA Bearer token
    ModelResolver->>ModelResolver: Populate modelInfoStore<br/>(in-memory)
    K8sAPI-->>APIKey: Watch labeled Secrets<br/>(bbr-managed=true)
    APIKey->>APIKey: Populate secretStore<br/>(in-memory)

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Client token

    Gateway->>ExtProc: Request body via ExtProc<br/>gRPC/9004, plaintext

    ExtProc->>ModelResolver: Process request
    ModelResolver->>ModelResolver: Resolve model name →<br/>provider + credentials<br/>(from modelInfoStore)
    ModelResolver->>ModelResolver: Write to CycleState:<br/>provider, model, creds ref

    ExtProc->>APITranslate: Process request
    APITranslate->>APITranslate: Read CycleState: provider type
    APITranslate->>APITranslate: Translate OpenAI format →<br/>Provider native format<br/>(Anthropic/Azure/Bedrock/Vertex)
    APITranslate->>APITranslate: Rewrite :path header<br/>Strip authorization header

    ExtProc->>APIKey: Process request
    APIKey->>APIKey: Read CycleState: credential ref
    APIKey->>APIKey: Lookup API key from secretStore
    APIKey->>APIKey: Inject provider auth header<br/>(Authorization/x-api-key/api-key)

    opt NeMo Guardrails enabled
        ExtProc->>NemoReq: Process request
        NemoReq->>NemoSvc: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP plaintext, no auth<br/>Request body (chat/MCP)
        NemoSvc-->>NemoReq: Allow / Block
        alt Request blocked
            NemoReq-->>ExtProc: 403 Forbidden
            ExtProc-->>Gateway: Immediate response
            Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: Mutated request<br/>(translated body + auth headers)

    Gateway->>LLM: Proxied request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Injected API key

    LLM-->>Gateway: Provider response

    Gateway->>ExtProc: Response body via ExtProc<br/>gRPC/9004

    ExtProc->>APITranslate: Process response
    APITranslate->>APITranslate: Translate provider format →<br/>OpenAI format<br/>Strip provider-specific fields

    opt NeMo Guardrails enabled
        ExtProc->>NemoResp: Process response
        NemoResp->>NemoSvc: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP plaintext, no auth<br/>Response body
        NemoSvc-->>NemoResp: Allow / Block
        alt Response blocked
            NemoResp-->>ExtProc: Replace with blocked msg
        end
    end

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: Mutated response<br/>(OpenAI format)
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443
